item.title: This Amazing Trick Will Show You How to Instantly Import .gpx Files Into Google Maps!
item.description: IV. Conclusion Introduction to Importing .gpx Files Into Google Maps Are you looking for a way to quickly and easily import .gpx files into Google Maps? If so, you’ve come to the right place! In this blog post, we’ll be going over a simple trick to help you do just that. What are .gpx Files? A .gpx file is a GPS Exchange Format file. It’s a type of file that is used to store and exchange GPS data.
